Package Files_format

Class Path2Kml

  • java.lang.Object
    • Files_format.Path2Kml

  • public class Path2Kml
extends java.lang.Object
    Path2Kml creates a kml from given paths from class solutions. with basic features such as creating color for each path and basic animation. NOTE: !!!!!the kml animation of packman motion is used by timespan in order to see it work you need both begin&end to work on slide!!!!!
